title: $:/plugins/nikorion/scroll-layout/settings
tags: $:/tags/ControlPanel/SettingsTab
caption: Scroll Layout
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

\whitespace trim

<h2>Scroll Layout — Settings</h2>

<p>Modified values create a config tiddler that overrides the default. The ↺ button deletes the tiddler and restores the default value.</p>

---

<h3>Scrollbar appearance</h3>

<p><em>Firefox (Gecko engine) only supports the "thin/auto/none" keyword and thumb/track colour on native scrollbars — width (px) and radius below only take effect in browsers built on Blink or WebKit (Chrome, Edge, Opera, Safari).</em></p>

<p><em>The story content width does not depend on the width mode: the plugin keeps the standard theme layout (Theme Tweaks story/sidebar metrics and the theme's gutters) and only repositions the river's scrollbar — its real width is measured automatically, the scrollbar stays glued to the story content and the neighbouring whitespace absorbs the difference.</em></p>

<table class="tc-pref-table tc-table-no-border">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>Width mode (Gecko/Firefox)</td>
<td><$select tiddler="$:/config/nikorion/scroll-layout/scrollbar-width-mode" field="text" default="thin">
<option value="thin">Thin</option>
<option value="auto">Auto</option>
<option value="none">None</option>
</$select></td>
<td><em>default:&nbsp;<code>thin</code></em></td>
<td><$list filter="[[$:/config/nikorion/scroll-layout/scrollbar-width-mode]is[tiddler]]"><$button tooltip="Restore default value">
<$action-deletetiddler $tiddler="$:/config/nikorion/scroll-layout/scrollbar-width-mode"/>↺</$button></$list></td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>Width (Blink/WebKit only)</td>
<td><$edit-text tiddler="$:/config/nikorion/scroll-layout/scrollbar-width" field="text" default="10px" tag="input" size="8"/></td>
<td><em>default:&nbsp;<code>10px</code></em></td>
<td><$list filter="[[$:/config/nikorion/scroll-layout/scrollbar-width]is[tiddler]]"><$button tooltip="Restore default value">
<$action-deletetiddler $tiddler="$:/config/nikorion/scroll-layout/scrollbar-width"/>↺</$button></$list></td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>Thumb radius (Blink/WebKit only)</td>
<td><$edit-text tiddler="$:/config/nikorion/scroll-layout/scrollbar-radius" field="text" default="8px" tag="input" size="8"/></td>
<td><em>default:&nbsp;<code>8px</code></em></td>
<td><$list filter="[[$:/config/nikorion/scroll-layout/scrollbar-radius]is[tiddler]]"><$button tooltip="Restore default value">
<$action-deletetiddler $tiddler="$:/config/nikorion/scroll-layout/scrollbar-radius"/>↺</$button></$list></td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>Thumb colour</td>
<td><$edit-text tiddler="$:/config/nikorion/scroll-layout/scrollbar-thumb-color" field="text" type="color" default="#5778d8" tag="input"/></td>
<td><em>default:&nbsp;<code>var(--tpc-primary)</code></em></td>
<td><$list filter="[[$:/config/nikorion/scroll-layout/scrollbar-thumb-color]is[tiddler]]"><$button tooltip="Restore default value">
<$action-deletetiddler $tiddler="$:/config/nikorion/scroll-layout/scrollbar-thumb-color"/>↺</$button></$list></td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>Thumb colour hover (Blink/WebKit only)</td>
<td><$edit-text tiddler="$:/config/nikorion/scroll-layout/scrollbar-thumb-hover-color" field="text" type="color" default="#5778d8" tag="input"/></td>
<td><em>default:&nbsp;<code>var(--tpc-primary)</code></em></td>
<td><$list filter="[[$:/config/nikorion/scroll-layout/scrollbar-thumb-hover-color]is[tiddler]]"><$button tooltip="Restore default value">
<$action-deletetiddler $tiddler="$:/config/nikorion/scroll-layout/scrollbar-thumb-hover-color"/>↺</$button></$list></td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>Track colour</td>
<td><$edit-text tiddler="$:/config/nikorion/scroll-layout/scrollbar-track-color" field="text" default="transparent" tag="input" size="20"/></td>
<td><em>default:&nbsp;<code>transparent</code></em></td>
<td><$list filter="[[$:/config/nikorion/scroll-layout/scrollbar-track-color]is[tiddler]]"><$button tooltip="Restore default value">
<$action-deletetiddler $tiddler="$:/config/nikorion/scroll-layout/scrollbar-track-color"/>↺</$button></$list></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>

